MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-1629. State ex rel. Automated Solutions Corp. v. Friedland.

Cuyahoga App. No. 92583, 2009-Ohio-3741. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
